Ing '''WAV''' (o '''WAVE'''), a pamikuyad king Waveform [[audio format]], [[audio file format]] standard ne ning [[Microsoft]] ampo ning [[International Business Machines|IBM]] para king pamanyimpan king audio bitstream kareng [[personal computer|PC]]. Kawangis ne ning paralan a [[Resource Interchange File Format|RIFF]] [[bitstream format]] para king pamanyimpan data kareng “chunks” (pira-pirasu), ania malapit ya king [[Interchange File Format|IFF]] da reng [[Amiga]] computer ampo ing [[Audio Interchange File Format|AIFF]] kareng [[Apple Macintosh|Macintosh]] computer. Iti ing manimunang format a magagamit kareng [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]] system para king e metagin (raw) ampong e mesiksik (uncompressed) a audio. Ing default bitstream encoding (itang magamit liban kaniti) yapin ing Microsoft [[Linear pulse code modulation|Pulse Code Modulation]] (PCM) format.  

